Package: command
Type: Package
Title: Process Command Line Arguments in a Function-Like Way
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: John Bryant
Maintainer: John Bryant <john@bayesiandemography.com>
Description: Create objects in the current environment
    based on arguments passed at the command line.
    Allows scripts to behave like functions, which
    can make workflows clearer and safer.
